      "html": "<p>也称为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">arrowhead</i>，意为“箭头”，15世纪晚期，源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of arrow \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/arrow\">arrow</a> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of head \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/head\">head</a>（名词）。古代挖掘出来的箭头被称为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">elf-arrows</i>（17世纪）。</p>"
